Package: OptiLHS
Type: Package
Title: Optimized Latin Hypercube Sampling for Soil Sampling Design
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Carlos Carbajal
Maintainer: Carlos Carbajal <cmcarbajall@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive Shiny application for optimizing soil sampling designs
    using conditioned Latin Hypercube Sampling (cLHS) and Random Forest optimization.
    Implements a three-module workflow: sample size optimization using KL divergence,
    Random Forest-based sampling optimization, and alternative site selection for
    inaccessible locations. Features a complete web interface with interactive maps,
    progress tracking, and export capabilities. Fixed UI loading issues in v0.1.1.
